From 48ca4ecdbfe0e536b0f2f981005450d787736ebb Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Mikhail Kshevetskiy <mikhail.kshevetskiy@iopsys.eu>
Date: Wed, 17 Jun 2026 08:29:44 +0300
Subject: [PATCH 08/19] pinctrl: airoha: add pin controller and gpio driver for
 AN7583 SoC

This patch adds U-Boot pin controller and gpio driver for Airoha AN7583 SoC.

Signed-off-by: Mikhail Kshevetskiy <mikhail.kshevetskiy@iopsys.eu>
Reviewed-by: David Lechner <dlechner@baylibre.com>
Signed-off-by: Matheus Sampaio Queiroga <srherobrine20@gmail.com>
